<sec>
<st>
Task states</st>
<p>

µC/OS-II is a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../857/6857.xml">
multitasking</link> operating system. Each task is an infinite loop and can be in any one of the following 5 states:
<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Dormant</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Ready</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Running</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

Waiting</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

<link>
Interrupt Service Routine</link></entry>
</list>
</p>

